1. *Cura* je šetala po parku. (The girl was walking through the park.)
2. Otac mu je govorio da se ponaša kao *cura*. (His father told him to behave like a girl.)
3. Njegov brat se ponašao kao da je on *cura*. (His brother was behaving like he was a girl.)
4. *Cure* su se smejale u parku. (The girls were laughing in the park.)
5. Kako je izgledala *cura* kad je izašla iz kuće? (How did the girl look when she came out of the house?)
6. *Curama* je bilo dozvoljeno da odu u školu. (The girls were allowed to go to school.)